ora Films]]\n|-\n|''[[Now That I Have You]]''||[[Laurenti M. Dyogi]]||[[John Lloyd Cruz]], [[Bea Alonzo]] ||Romance||[[Star Cinema]]\n|-\n|''[[Otso Otso Pamela-mela Wan]]''|| [[Jerry Lopez Sineneng]] ||[[Bayani Agbayani]], [[Vhong Navarro]]|| Comedy ||[[Star Cinema]]\n|-\n|''[[Panaghoy sa Suba]]''||[[Cesar Montano]]||[[Cesar Montano]], [[Juliana Palermo]]|| ||[[CM Productions]]\n|-\n|''[[Sabel (film)|Sabel]]''||  ||[[Judy Ann Santos]]|| ||[[Regal Films]]\n|-\n|''[[Santa Santita]]''||[[Laurice Guillen]]||[[Angelica Panganiban]], [[Jericho Rosales]]||Drama||[[Unitel Pictures]]\n|-\n|''[[Sigaw]]''|| Yam Laranas || [[Richard Gutierrez]], [[Angel Locsin]]|| Suspense/Horror ||[[Viva Films]]\n|-\n|''[[So Happy Together (film)|So Happy Together]]''|| [[Joel Lamangan]] || [[Kris Aquino]], [[Eric Quizon]] || Comedy ||[[Regal Films]]\n|-\n|''[[Spirit of the Glass]]''|| || ||Horror ||[[Canary Films]]\n|-\n|''[[Volta (film)]]''||  ||[[Ai-Ai de las Alas]] || Fantasy, Comedy ||[[Star Cinema]]\n|}\n\n==2005==\n{{main|List of Philippine films of 2005}}\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Title !! Director !! Cast !! Genre !! Studio\n|-\n| {{Year header}} | '''[[2005 in film|2005]]'''\n|-\n|''[[Ako, Legal Wife: Mano Po 4?!]]''||[[Joel Lamangan]]||[[Zsa Zsa Padilla]], [[Rufa Mae Quinto]], [[Cherry Pie Picache]], [[Jay Manalo]]|| ||[[Regal Films]]\n|-\n|''[[Ang Pagdadalaga ni Maximo Oliveros]]''||[[Auraeus Solito]]||[[Nathan Lopez]], [[Soliman Cruz]], [[JR Valentin]] & [[Ping Medina]] ||Drama/Comedy||[[Unitel Pictures]]\n|-\n|''[[Bahay ni Lola 2]]''||[[Joven Tan]]||[[Cherry Pie Picache]], [[Dingdong Dantes]], [[Karylle]]||Horror||[[Regal Films]]\n|-\n|''[[Bathhouse (film)]]''|| || || ||[[Homosexuality]]\n|-\n|''[[Birhen ng Manaoag]]''|| ||[[Albert Martinez]], [[Cherry Pie Picache]], [[Eddie Garcia]], [[Joyce Jimenez]] ||Drama ||[[Cine Suerte, Inc.]]\n|-\n|''[[Can This Be Love]]''||[[Jose Javier Reyes]]||[[Hero Angeles]], [[Sandara Park]]||Romance||[[Star Cinema]]\n|-\n| ''[[Chavit (film)]]'