ina Bonnevie]], [[Ricky Davao]]|| ||[[Star Cinema]]\n|-\n|''[[Bahid]]''|| ||[[Eddie Garcia]]|| ||[[Jagss Entertainment]]\n|-\n|''[[Batas ng Lansangan]]''|| ||[[Fernando Poe Jr]], [[Dina Bonnevie]], [[Kaye Abad]], [[Charlie Davao]], [[Roi Vinzon]], [[Dick Israel]]|| ||[[Viva Films]]\n|-\n|''[[Dekada '70 (film)|Dekada '70]]''|| ||[[Vilma Santos]], [[Christopher de Leon]], [[Piolo Pascual]]||Drama||[[Star Cinema]]\n|-\n|''[[Diskarte]]''|| || || ||[[Maverick Films]]\n|-\n|''[[D' Uragons]]''|| ||[[Andrew E]], [[Eddie Garcia]]|| ||[[Viva Films]]\n|-\n|''[[Forevermore (film)|Forevermore]]''|| ||[[Kristine Hermosa]], [[Jericho Rosales]]|| ||[[Star Cinema]]\n|-\n|''[[Gamitan]]''|| [[Quark Henares]] || Maui Taylor, Wendell Ramos, Jordan Herrera || Action, Drama ||[[Viva Films]]\n|-\n|''[[Got 2 Believe]]''||[[Olivia M. Lamasan]]||[[Claudine Barretto]], [[Rico Yan]]|| ||[[Star Cinema]]\n|-\n|''[[Hula Mo...Huli Ko]]'' || Edgar Vinarao || [[Rudy Fernandez (actor)|Rudy Fernandez]] and [[Rufa Mae Quinto]] || Comedy ||Reflection Films\n|-\n|''[[Home Along da Riber]]''|| [[Eric Quizon]]|| [[Dolphy]], [[Jolina Magdangal]], [[Zsa Zsa Padilla]], [[Vandolph]], [[Eddie Gutierrez (actor)|Eddie Gutierrez]], Long Mejia, James Blanco, Boy2 Quizon, Michelle Quizon, Palito|| Comedy || RVQ Productions\n|-\n|''[[I Think I'm in Love]]''|| || || ||[[Regal Films]]\n|-\n|''[[Jeannie, Bakit Ngayon Ka Lang?]]''|| [[Ike Jarlego Jr]] || Robin Padilla, Judy Ann Santos, King Alcala || Drama ||[[Viva Films]]\n|-\n|''[[JOLOGS]]''||[[Gilbert G. Perez]]||[[Diether Ocampo]], [[Patrick Garcia]], [[Vhong Navarro]], [[Onemig Bondoc]], [[Dominic Ochoa]], [[Assunta De Rossi]], [[John Prats]], [[Jodi Sta. Maria]], [[Julia Clarete]], [[Baron Geisler]], [[Michelle Bayle]]|| ||[[Star Cinema]]\n|-\n|''[[Kailangan Kita]]''||[[Rory Quintos]]||[[Claudine Barretto]], [[Aga Muhlach]]|| ||[[Star Cinema]]\n|-\n| ''[[Kung Ikaw Ay Isang Panaginip]]'' || ||[[Jolina Magdangal]]|| ||[[Star Cinema]]\n|-\n| ''[[Laman (film)|Laman]]'' 