{"title_page": "Supalonely", "text_new": "{{short description|2019 single by Benee}}\n{{Infobox song\n|name=Supalonely\n|type=single\n|artist=[[Benee]] featuring [[Gus Dapperton]]\n|EP=[[Stella & Steve]]\n|released=6 December 2019\n|format={{hlist|[[Music download|Digital download]]|[[Streaming media|streaming]]}}\n|genre={{hlist|[[Pop music|Pop]]<ref name=\"id\"/>|[[alternative pop]]<ref name=\"Idolator\"/>}}\n|length=3:43\n|label=[[Republic Records]]\n|writer={{hlist|[[Gus Dapperton|Brendan Patrick Rice]]|[[Jenna Andrews]]|[[Kidz in Space|Josh Fountain]]|[[Benee|Stella Rose Bennett]]}}\n|producer={{hlist|Josh Fountain|Brendan Patrick Rice}}\n|chronology=[[Benee]]\n|prev_title=[[Monsta (song)|Monsta]]\n|prev_year=2019\n|year=2019\n|misc={{external music video|type=single|{{YouTube|Rb6Scz-5YOs|Supalonely}}}}\n}}\n\n\"'''Supalonely'''\" (pronounced {{IPAc-en|s|u\u02d0|p|\u0259|l|o\u028a|n|l|i\u02d0}} {{respell|SOO-p\u0259-lone-lee}}) is a song by New Zealand singer [[Benee]] featuring American singer [[Gus Dapperton]]. It was initially released as a song on her second extended play ''[[Stella & Steve]]'' on 15 November 2019, before becoming the EP's third and final single on 6 December 2019.<ref name=\"Bongmines\">{{cite web|url=https://www.bongminesentertainment.com/benee-supalonely-gus-dapperton/ |title=BENEE releases an upbeat alternative-pop tune, entitled, \"Supalonely\", featuring Gus Dapperton |author=Thomson, Zangba |date=3 December 2019|website=Bongmines Entertainment|accessdate= 24 January 2020}}</ref><ref name=\"pilerats\">{{cite web|url=http://pilerats.com/written/light-easy/must-listen-singles-benee-spacey-jane-young-franco-more/|title=This Week's Must-Listen Singles: BENEE, Spacey Jane, Young Franco + more|last=Davies|first=Hayden|date=11 December 2019|website=PILERATS|url-status=live|accessdate=15 March 2020}}</ref> The song gained popularity after spawning a viral dance challenge on the online video-sharing platform [[TikTok]] in March 2020.<ref name=\"Idolator\">{{Cite web|url=https://www.idolator.com/7907879/future-hit-benees-supalonely-is-absolutely-irresistible|title=Future Hit: BENEE's \"Supalonely\" Is Absolutely Irresistible|last=Wass|first=Mike|date=10 March 2020|website=[[Idolator (website)|Idolator]]|url-status=live|access-date=13 March 2020}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.clashmusic.com/videos/benees-supalonely-is-ultra-infectious|title=BENEE's 'Supalonely' Is Ultra-Infectious|last=Murray|first=Robin|date=6 March 2020|website=[[Clash (magazine)|Clash]]|access-date=13 March 2020}}</ref> The song was certified Gold on its second week on the [[New Zealand Top 40]]. It peaked on the top 25 of countries such as the UK, Canada, Netherlands, Australia, Ireland, Norway, Austria, Finland and Denmark.\n\n== Critical reception ==\nOn his [[Apple Music]] show, [[Elton John]] described \"Supalonely\" as a \"smash record\", and further described Benee as \"an amazing young artist\" who \"writes really brilliantly\".<ref>{{Cite news|last=Barton|first=Monika|url=https://www.newshub.co.nz/home/entertainment/2020/03/elton-john-raves-about-amazing-benee-confesses-he-s-crazy-about-six60-on-apple-music-show.html|title=Elton John raves about 'amazing' Benee, confesses he's 'crazy about' Six60 on Apple Music show|date=6 March 2020|work=Newshub|access-date=15 March 2020|url-status=live|language=en}}</ref> Ariana Marsh from [[I-D|''i-D'']] wrote that the \"sunny pop\" song \"turns your typical breakup song on its head\".<ref name=\"id\">{{Cite web|url=https://i-d.vice.com/en_uk/article/jgeg8b/benee-and-gus-dapperton-turn-breakup-blues-into-sunny-pop-on-supalonely|title=BENEE and Gus Dapperton turn breakup blues into sunny pop on Supalonely|last=Marsh|first=Ariana|date=4 February 2020|website=[[i-D]]|language=en|url-status=live|access-date=15 March 2020}}</ref> The song was described by Glenn Rowley of ''[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]'' as \"a quirky, knowing ode to the art of loneliness\".<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop/8550207/benee-supalonely-video-tour-dates|title=Benee Is 'Supalonely' in Colorful New Video, Announces North American Tour: See the Dates|last=Rowley|first=Glenn|date=5 February 2020|website=Billboard|url-status=live|access-date=15 March 2020}}</ref>\n\n== Charts ==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\"| Chart (2020)\n! scope=\"col\"| Peak<br />position\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Argentina ([[Argentina Hot 100]])<ref>{{cite web|url=https://billboard.com.ar/chart/2020-04-18-2-2-2-2-2-2-2-2-2-2-2-2-2-2-2-2-2/|title=Billboard Argentina Hot 100 \u2013 Semana del 19 de abril|language=Spanish|accessdate=16 April 2020|work=[[Billboard Argentina]]}}</ref>\n| 71\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Australia ([[ARIA Charts|ARIA]])<ref name=\"ARIA\">{{cite web|url=http://www.ariacharts.com.au/charts/singles-chart|title=ARIA Australian Top 50 Singles|publisher=[[Australian Recording Industry Association]]|date=6 April 2020|accessdate=4 April 2020}}</ref>\n| 8\n|-\n{{single chart|Austria|15|artist=Benee feat. Gus Dapperton|song=Supalonely|rowheader=true|accessdate=2 April 2020}}\n|-\n{{single chart|Flanders|12|artist=Benee feat. Gus Dapperton|song=Supalonely|rowheader=true|accessdate=10 April 2020}}\n|-\n{{single chart|Wallonia|37|artist=Benee feat. Gus Dapperton|song=Supalonely|rowheader=true|accessdate=17 April 2020}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Canada ([[Canadian Hot 100]])<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/charts/search?artistname=Benee&chartcode=CAN|title=Benee, CAN|work=[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]|accessdate=8 April 2020}}</ref>\n| 10\n|-\n{{single chart|Czech Republic|35|year=2020|week=15|rowheader=true|accessdate=15 April 2020}}\n|-\n{{single chart|Czechdigital|19|year=2020|week=16|rowheader=true|accessdate=21 April 2020}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Denmark ([[Tracklisten]])<ref>{{cite web|url=http://hitlisten.nu/default.asp?w=13&y=2020&list=t40|title=Track Top-40 Uge 13, 2020|publish